item.title: Videos and Trails
item.description: Videos and Trails 1. cartolastd - 696 observations - 19 timesteps - 17 dimensions - 5 classes ... The dataset was scrapped from the Brazilian fantasy soccer platform Cartola and represents the second turn of the 2017 championship. The scrapper source can be found at https://github.com/henriquepgomide/caRtola. To make the dataset smoother, the dimensions were cumulatively averaged. 2. cifar10cnn - 1000 observations - 30 timesteps - 10 dimensions - 10 classes .
